CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FA group of bereaved families have
OL,8,Fwelcomed the appointment of a
OL,9,Fchairwoman for the independent review
OL,10,Fof maternity services at a hospital
OL,11,Ftrust as they stressed that the
OL,12,Finvestigation must include all harmed
OL,13,Ffamilies.
OL,15,FSussex Truth for Our Babies group said
OL,16,Fmore than 60 families in the county
OL,17,Fhave been affected by maternity care
OL,18,Ffailings.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe families met Wes Streeting in
OL,8,FBrighton on Wednesday, where he
OL,9,Fconfirmed that senior midwife and
OL,10,Finvestigator Donna Ockenden, who the
OL,11,Ffamilies wanted to lead the
OL,12,Finvestigation, will chair the review
OL,13,Finto maternity care at University
OL,14,FHospitals Sussex NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,16,FMr Streeting, who announced the review
OL,17,Flast June, has "listened to the
OL,18,Fcampaigning families", the group said.
OL,26,@yD@POUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"This has been a long, exhausting and
OL,8,Fdeeply emotional fight for all of us,"
OL,9,Fbereaved mother Katie Fowler said in a
OL,10,Fstatement on behalf of Sussex Truth
OL,11,Ffor Our Babies group.
OL,13,FMs Fowler's daughter Abigail Fowler
OL,14,FMiller died two days after being born
OL,15,Fat the Royal Sussex County Hospital in
OL,16,FBrighton in January 2022.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FAn inquest concluded she would likely
OL,8,Fhave survived if her mother had
OL,9,Freceived medical treatment sooner,
OL,10,Fwith Ms Fowler also going into cardiac
OL,11,Farrest.
OL,13,FThe statement continued: "As a group,
OL,14,Fwe have been calling for this review
OL,15,Ffor two years, all while living with
OL,16,Fdevastating loss and harm caused to us
OL,17,Fand our babies.
OL,26,@uD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"Today's announcement represents a
OL,8,Fsignificant and welcome step forward.
OL,9,FWe are grateful that Wes Streeting has
OL,10,Flistened to campaigning families and
OL,11,Frecognised the need to appoint Donna
OL,12,FOckenden to lead the review.
OL,14,F"While the full scope of the review is
OL,15,Fyet to be agreed, Mr Streeting was
OL,16,Freceptive to the arguments we made as
OL,17,Fto why a full, inclusive review is
OL,18,Fneeded to ensure that no family is
OL,19,Fleft behind.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"A review that does not include all
OL,8,Fharmed and bereaved families cannot
OL,9,Fdeliver the truth or accountability
OL,10,Fthat is so desperately needed. Lessons
OL,11,Fwill be missed, and opportunities to
OL,12,Fprevent future harm could be lost.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"This review gives us hope that we
OL,8,Fwill finally get answers we have been
OL,9,Fseeking, not just for our own
OL,10,Ffamilies, but for every family that
OL,11,Fhas been affected. It is about
OL,12,Faccountability, but it's also about
OL,13,Fworking to ensure that no other family
OL,14,Fhas to endure what we have been
OL,15,Fthrough."
OL,17,FMr Streeting told reporters: "I don't
OL,18,Fmind saying this (preparation for the
OL,19,Freview) has taken too long, and I've
OL,20,Fcertainly reflected on that.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@IO]yD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"It was important to me to make sure
OL,8,Fthat we got the scope of this right."
OL,10,FHe added that he had not "ruled out" a
OL,11,Ffull public inquiry into maternity
OL,12,Fcare across the country.
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Health Secretary
OL,15,Fsaid: "Donna Ockenden has earned the
OL,16,Ftrust of families across the country
OL,17,Fthrough her tireless work to uncover
OL,18,Fthe truth and drive lasting change in
OL,19,Fmaternity care. I know she will bring
OL,20,Fthat same dedication to Sussex.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@eO]rD@ZOUrD@dO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"To the families in Sussex, your
OL,8,Fdetermination to seek answers not just
OL,9,Ffor yourselves, but for every family
OL,10,Fwho comes after you, is so important.
OL,11,FThis review has my full personal
OL,12,Fcommitment, and I will ensure we get
OL,13,Fthe answers and deliver the change you
OL,14,Fdeserve."
OL,16,FMs Ockenden said it was an "honour" to
OL,17,Fbe asked to chair the review.
OL,19,F"I am absolutely aware of the
OL,20,Fresponsibility I have to the families
OL,21,Fand babies across Sussex," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@IO]xD@\OUxD@cO]{D@AOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"My priority will be to listen
OL,8,Fcarefully to harmed and bereaved
OL,9,Ffamilies and to engage comprehensively
OL,10,Facross communities and with staff on
OL,11,Fthe ground here in Sussex."
OL,13,FLiz Charlton, a mother who said there
OL,14,Fwere "failings" in her care which led
OL,15,Fto the death of her baby Hazel at
OL,16,FWorthing Hospital in 2021, told the
OL,17,FPress Association ahead of the meeting
OL,18,Fthat an opt-out independent review by
OL,19,FMs Ockenden would give her
OL,20,Faccountability and justice.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@[O]vD@FOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"The only way you can have clear
OL,8,Fchange is to have the most efficient,
OL,9,Feffective review done by someone that
OL,10,Fhas an evidence base of doing it, that
OL,11,Fknows how to do it, that's done it
OL,12,Fwell before," Ms Charlton said.
OL,14,F"So for me, it will give me
OL,15,Faccountability and justice, I think,
OL,16,Fand overall really change for the
OL,17,Ffuture."
OL,19,FLast month Ms Ockenden was named as
OL,20,Fchairwoman of an investigation into
OL,21,Fmaternity services in Leeds.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@MO]vD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FShe is also examining how hundreds of
OL,8,Fbabies died or were injured in the
OL,9,Fcare of Nottingham University
OL,10,FHospitals Trust, with a final report
OL,11,Fexpected this summer.
OL,13,FIt follows her review into mother and
OL,14,Fbaby deaths at Shrewsbury and Telford
OL,15,FHospital NHS Trust.
OL,17,FThe chief executive officer of UH
OL,18,FSussex said the trust welcomes the
OL,19,Fappointment of Ms Ockenden, but added
OL,20,Fthat there is "more to do".
OL,26,@|D@OOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FDr Andy Heeps said: "The loss of a
OL,8,Fbaby is the worst thing that a parent
OL,9,Fcan imagine, let alone experience. For
OL,10,Fany family who has been through such a
OL,11,Ftrauma, I am deeply sorry.
OL,26,@oD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"We welcome today's announcement that
OL,8,Fa chair has been appointed to lead the
OL,9,Findependent review into Sussex
OL,10,Fmaternity services. We will work
OL,11,Fopenly and transparently with the
OL,12,FDonna Ockenden review team, and with
OL,13,Ffamilies who have used our services,
OL,14,Fbecause we believe external scrutiny
OL,15,Fcan help drive improvement. We hope
OL,16,Fthis announcement will provide some
OL,17,Freassurance to families, and we will
OL,18,Fdo everything we can to support the
OL,19,Freview and help families get the
OL,20,Fanswers they seek.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"I also want to reassure families in
OL,8,FSussex about our maternity services
OL,9,Ftoday. We know that trust has to be
OL,10,Fearned through the care we provide and
OL,11,Fthe action we take, and we have made
OL,12,Fimportant changes in recent years to
OL,13,Fstrengthen the safety and quality of
OL,14,Fthe care we provide to people now.
OL,15,FThat work never ends, and our staff
OL,16,Fremain deeply committed to providing
OL,17,Fsafe, compassionate care to every
OL,18,Fwoman, baby and family who uses our
OL,19,Fservices.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
