OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776366672
OL,3,CParents of babies who died in Sussex
OL,4,Cwin fight for midwife to lead
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"We know there is more to do, and we
OL,8,Fwill keep working with openness,
OL,9,Fhumility and determination to deliver
OL,10,Fthe safest and best care possible."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@cO]
